60
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:35,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Myung Rang.</font>

61
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku. Itu terlalu berlebihan.</font>

62
00:03:39,930 --> 00:03:41,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi Manajer Jung,</font>

63
