<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahku?</font>

80
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:30,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahku mungkin orang kaya.</font>

81
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:32,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah?</font>

82
